Joah8-thiN i2-keng kun7 lah.  Khong- khi3 jit8-jit8 na2 sio-lo7.  Koh bo5 ku2 chiu7 toa7 joah8.  Joah8 na7 kau3 tai7-ke chiu7 kan- khou2. Sui-jian5 chheng7 joah8-saN chhut- lat8 iat8 siN3, a2-si7 chiah8 peng chui2 ia7 si7 boe7 chhiu-chhin3. Jit8-thau5 chit8-e7 iam7 chhu3-lai7 liam5-piN jiat8 phong2-phong2. Chhu3-teng2 phak8 chit8-e7 sio, sio-khi3 tui3 teng2-bin7 hah loh8-lai5, bo5 ku2 koaN7 chiu7 chhap-chhap tih, siN3 koh khah iat8 to boe7 chhiu-chhin3.
Chhu3-lai7 phak8 kau3 jiat8 kun2-kun2, gin2- na2 toa7-soe3 tai7-ke ia7 si7 kan-khou2.  Hip joah8 liau2 piN7 ia7 liam5-piN kau3. U7-e5 siN pui3-a2, u7-e5 siN liap8-a2, u7-e5 hoat-khi2 jiat8- cheng3, joah8 kau3, cheng3-thau5 ia7 kau3.
TaN m7-chai u7 sim2-mih8 ho2 hoat-tou7 thang hou7 chhu3-lai7 khah liang5,khah chhiu-chhin3 bo5 ? U7, u7 chit8 e5 ho2 hoat- tou7. Chhu3-lai7 tioh8 teng3 thian-lo5-pan2. Chhu3 na7 bo5 thian-lo5-pan2, chhu3-teng2 phak8 sio, sio khi3 liam5-piN hah loh8-lai5. Chhu3-lai7 na7 u7 thian-lo5-pan2 sio khi3 chiu7 hah boe7 loh8-lai5. Sio khi3 ka-ki7 oe7 tui3 ian-lau5 chhut-khi3. An2-ni chhu3-lai7 khah bo5 sio khi3. Chhu3 na7 chhong3 thian-lo5- pan2 chi3-chio2 oe7 ke chhiu-chhin3 5 tou7. An2-ni m7-si7 sio2-khoa2. Koh chit8 hang7. Thian-lo5-pan2 m7-na7 oe7 hou7 chhu3-lai7 khah liang5, u7 thian-lo5-pan2 chhu3-lai7 ia7 oe7 khah chheng-khi3, khah boe7 eng-ia. Koh-chai3 ke ho2 khoaN3 chin-choe7.
